    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;The Hypertext Transfer Protocol (HTTP) is a stateless application- level protocol for distributed, collaborative, hypertext information systems.  This document defines range requests and the rules for constructing and combining responses to those requests.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
